{"tid":1517700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[分化撚？] 義士就嚟畀你哋口中講嘅自己友出賣喇","createTime":"2019-08-30T04:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T06:09:57.000Z","uid":313463,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eefe28d13c71f8ad16e5f7783af77a691d47f797","tid":1517700,"uid":313463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3s2ubuT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3s2ubuT.png&h=31873422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPGR9hW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPGR9hW.png&h=b377fa63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一圖講晒，各位自行判斷<br />\n楊岳橋根本就心虛唔敢回應大家嘅問題，咁多人留言問佢同一個問題，佢會睇唔到？<br />\n泛粉唔好再話佢已經開咗記者會啦，佢個所謂記者會根本冇交代過佢支持《香港人權及民主法案》邊條條文，佢只係支持其中一項，就話自己係支持都得㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n到底香港人係咪仲要繼續相信泛民啊？佢哋係推班義士去死㗎，講事實就話人分化，叫佢正面回應就話人分化，我哋對佢有懷疑，問清楚都好應該啊，佢哋有咁多前科就係人都知㗎啦<br />\n佢如果係行得正企得正，洗乜喺到玩語言偽術，都唔正面回應佢詳細係支持《香港人權及民主法案》邊條條文？"},{"pid":"5e38a05cda5da97a97023daf2c025c715b368f17","tid":1517700,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8m6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=8829a32d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8m6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=e129f681\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs